face2face.statistics.check_distribution.distribution_tupel_combinations¶

face2face.statistics.check_distribution.distribution_tupel_combinations(distribution_list, fit)¶

Searches the best fitting distribution

Compares every distribution included in this package against each other and returns every combination as a list of tupels. The normalized loglikelihood is also included in the tupel.

Parameters

  • distribution_list (list) – Contains a list of strings with every distribution included in this package.

  • fit (Fit object) – Fit objected for the given data set.

Returns

list_for_distribution_tupels – Contains tupels with the comparison of every distribution that is included in the package.

Return type

list

See also

face2face.statistics.check_distribution.search_best_fit_distribution()
